#12501
castle sentry~
a castle sentry~
A castle sentry stands posted here at the gate to New Hope Castle.
~
One of the guards to the gate of the castle of New Hope, this man shows no
notice to your attention of him, but has probably been keeping a watch on
you as far as you've been in sight of the castle, as so he does for all
passerbys to the castle.  Clad head to toe in the royal armors and weaponry
of the guards of New Hope, he looks both proud and grim, like he's ready
to lay down his life for his homeland, though worn by boredom due to
the ever-decreasing need for guards, as things here are peaceful and
no threat has made it's way here in longer then his own lifespan so far.
~
