#12530
drawbridge lever~
the drawbridge lever~
The drawbridge lever is set upon the south wall here, to the side of the doorway.~
~
37 1073741824 0
0 0 0 0
1 0 0 0
> push_prog 100~
if isnpc($n)
then
mpclosepassage 12510 0
mpclosepassage 12511 2
mpopenpassage 12511 12599 5
mpecho The castle sentry pushes the drawbridge lever.  *Click*  The drawbridge raises up...
mpat 12511 mpecho The drawbridge raises up...
mpat 12510 mpecho The drawbridge raises up...
else
if time($n) > 6
or time($n) < 20
then
mpechoat $n The castle sentry tells you that the drawbridge is not to go down until daybreak, and to leave it alone.
mpat 12512 mpforce sentry pull lever
endif
endif
~
> pull_prog 100~
if isnpc($n)
then
mpopenpassage 12511 12510 2
mpopenpassage 12510 12511 0
mpclosepassage 12511 5
mpecho The castle sentry pulls the drawbridge lever.  *Click*  The drawbridge lowers down...
mpat 12511 mpecho The drawbridge lowers down...
mpat 12510 mpecho The drawbridge lowers down...
else
if time($n) < 6
or time($n) > 20
then
mpechoat $n The castle sentry tells you that the drawbridge is not to go down until daybreak, and to leave it alone.
mpat 12512 mpforce sentry push lever
endif
endif
~
